Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是土星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.89,0:01:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有光环
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.44,0:01:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:39.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好耀眼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用肉眼也能清晰地看到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Spica
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.69,0:01:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}处女座的α星 是处女座中最亮的恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.24,0:01:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是处女座的α星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.07,0:01:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在日本也被叫做珍珠星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.41,0:01:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍珠星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:53.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那看起来薄薄的一层是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:54.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银河
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.54,0:01:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的很薄呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.00,0:02:01.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在饭能 街上有灯光呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.30,0:02:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.68,0:02:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.31,0:02:14.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不知道去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.40,0:02:21.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你讨厌萤火虫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:25.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊 咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 葵 日向 要不要去看萤火虫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有个能看到很多萤火虫的绝佳地点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.20,0:02:34.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很…很多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.12,0:02:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很多的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.96,0:02:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小时候喜欢萤火虫喜欢到想要变成萤火虫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想变成萤火虫…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.55,0:02:45.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真像是心夏会做的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.59,0:02:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈经常带我去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.80,0:02:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤火虫和星空 闪闪发光 就像漂浮在宇宙中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 日向 去吧去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:02:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.73,0:03:02.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也联系下枫同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.02,0:03:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待能看到萤火虫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.12,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(658,206)}不可思议的萤火虫物语
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.45,0:03:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浴衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家决定一起穿着浴衣去看萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.58,0:03:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是在名栗湖那边 妈妈你有浴衣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.37,0:03:22.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有是有 可能有点大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃完饭穿穿看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.92,0:03:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:32.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 葵小时候也在名栗湖那看过一次萤火虫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.26,0:03:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得是幼儿园的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.22,0:03:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我们家和日向家一起去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.81,0:03:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤火虫吗 好像模模糊糊的能想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 去那边看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.36,0:03:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:56.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.17,0:04:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会有萤火虫妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.77,0:04:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是跟梦混淆了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵不记得了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.82,0:04:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种东西怎么可能存在啊 日向真是个小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.41,0:04:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会被嘲笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:41.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她连我都忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.92,0:04:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:50.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和日向走散了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:55.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向哭得很厉害呢 一发不可收拾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:05:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次逗逗她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了对了 那时候葵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.15,0:05:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊 是妖精小姐带我们来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤火虫妖精小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.57,0:05:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是看到了什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 不要哭 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.43,0:05:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来 这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想起来了 那时确实是有萤火虫妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.32,0:05:54.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:06:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖精？那种东西怎么可能会有啊 真是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.20,0:06:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会被她这样嘲笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就是这种人 还是别说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:17.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.51,0:06:21.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人靠衣装 葵靠浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.19,0:06:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那句话我原封不动的还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说以前去看萤火虫的时候 你哭得很厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.65,0:06:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵你记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.45,0:06:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是听妈妈说的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.41,0:06:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会是不记得萤火虫妖怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不记得萤火虫妖精了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不要说了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.63,0:06:58.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵和日向都很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.89,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是妈妈的旧衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.35,0:07:11.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心夏那件浴衣是哪来的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.56,0:07:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 这是我自己缝的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太厉害了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从以前开始 妈妈就给我做了很多衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.70,0:07:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也学着她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}各位 久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.91,0:07:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 枫…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿着太普通了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 大家真有干劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.59,0:07:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我打电话告诉你要穿浴衣集合了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.46,0:07:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 不要在意 不要在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,饭能还有这种地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.45,0:08:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是欣赏萤火虫的绝佳地点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小时候来的地方大概是这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人变得相当多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.17,0:08:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去人少一点的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.51,0:08:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢慢变黑了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.18,0:08:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这气氛感觉就算出现什么也不会奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.02,0:08:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要说奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能会有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.70,0:08:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵以前也看见过的吧 萤火虫妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.66,0:08:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢 日向
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.37,0:08:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看见的是萤火虫妖精吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你傻吗 哪里会有妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.37,0:08:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛 妖怪才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.92,0:09:01.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漆黑一片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:21.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看那
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.39,0:09:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日向 上面 上面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天空有星星
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地上有萤火虫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.32,0:10:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是在宇宙一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.24,0:10:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在星海中遨游
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然这么美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:15.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.08,0:10:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现什么也不奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.93,0:10:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家回家的时候小心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.89,0:10:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.40,0:10:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来 心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:10:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我买便当了 来吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.15,0:10:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤火虫怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闪闪的非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.45,0:10:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈一起去就好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.41,0:10:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法啊 有工作嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得是在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.59,0:11:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:11.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你穿着这个 一起去看过萤火虫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.18,0:11:18.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我说想成为萤火虫 妈妈给我做的玩偶服
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萤 萤 萤火虫来呀
